	<description><![CDATA[

Extension to the _Full text search_ app to index your users' files.

	]]>
	</description>
	<version>32.0.0</version>
	<licence>agpl</licence>
	<author>Maxence Lange</author>
	<namespace>Files_FullTextSearch</namespace>
